---
// SplitFeature.astro
---
<section class="section split-section">
  <div class="container container-split">
    <div class="split-left card dark-card">
      <div class="shield-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
      <h2>100% Anti-Detect — Akun Kamu <span class="text-gradient">AMAN</span></h2>
      <p class="desc">
        Sistem kami dibangun secara eksklusif mengikuti ketentuan dari TikTok Studio secara organik.
        Menghindari blokir massal dan proxy detector sehingga kamu tidak perlu takut kena penalti atau shadowban seperti pada bot lainnya.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="split-right">
      <div class="card right-card h-effect">
        <div class="r-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Browser Anti-Fingerprint & RPA</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Tidak menggunakan API cloud yang berisiko, melainkan kombinasi browser anti-detecting fingerprint khusus dan RPA (Robotic Process Automation) software agar akun tetap aman.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card right-card h-effect">
        <div class="r-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌐</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
            Software Khusus
            <span style="display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; color: var(--text-muted);" aria-label="Tersedia untuk Mac dan Windows">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                <path d="M0 93.7l183.6-25.3v177.4H0V93.7zm0 324.6l183.6 25.3V268.4H0v149.9zm203.8 28L448 480V268.4H203.8v177.9zm0-380.6v180.1H448V32L203.8 65.7z"/>
              </svg>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 384 512" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                <path d="M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 16.4-64.4 50-84.8-18.8-26.9-47.2-41.7-84.7-44.6-35.5-2.8-74.3 20.7-88.5 20.7-15 0-49.4-19.7-76.4-19.7C63.3 141.2 4 184.8 4 273.5q0 39.3 14.4 81.2c12.8 36.7 59 126.7 107.2 125.2 25.2-.6 43-17.9 75.8-17.9 31.8 0 48.3 17.9 76.4 17.9 48.6-.7 90.4-82.5 102.6-119.3-65.2-30.7-61.7-90-61.7-91.9zm-56.6-164.2c27.3-32.4 24.8-61.9 24-72.5-24.1 1.4-52 16.4-67.9 34.9-17.5 19.8-27.8 44.3-25.6 71.9 26.1 2 49.9-11.4 69.5-34.3z"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Software ini perlu diinstall di PC atau Laptop Windows atau MAC Os Anda. Sangat mumpuni untuk mengeksekusi upload masal ke banyak akun tanpa henti secara instan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="promo-box">
        🔥 <strong>Promo Spesial:</strong> Akses Selamanya - SEKALI BAYAR
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .split-section {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
  }

  .container-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .dark-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-card) 0%, var(--dark-violet) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 60px 50px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.5);
  }

  .shield-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .dark-card h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8 0%, #818cf8 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .dark-card .desc {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .split-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .right-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 30px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .r-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    background: #eef2ff;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .right-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .h-effect:hover {
    transform: translateX(-10px);
  }

  .promo-box {
    margin-top: 10px;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--accent-red);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .container-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .dark-card {
      padding: 40px 28px;
    }
    .dark-card h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .h-effect:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .split-section { padding: 48px 0; }
    .dark-card { padding: 32px 20px; }
    .dark-card h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .shield-icon { width: 64px; height: 64px; font-size: 2rem; border-radius: 16px; }
    .right-card { padding: 20px 16px; gap: 14px; }
    .r-icon { padding: 10px; font-size: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; }
    .right-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; }
    .right-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; }
    .promo-box { padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0; }
  }
</style>
